<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="9ef3e3aa-d22c-4bc6-99ba-9d5a9a583c51" >

    <h2>When working alone is high or medium risk </h2> 
<p>There are some activities and/or tasks that are necessary and permitted but the supervisor needs to determine if working alone or in isolation is:</p> 
<ul> 
 <li>high risk and strictly prohibited by law; or</li> 
 <li>high or medium risk and requires a safety plan.</li> 
</ul>
    





</div>
<script>$(document).ready(function(){addCoursePopover("#9ef3e3aa-d22c-4bc6-99ba-9d5a9a583c51");});</script></div>

				

				
