                            What are the responsibilities of supervisors and workers?
                        </a>
                    </h3>
                    
                </div>
                <!-- Accordion Body -->
                <div tabindex="0" id="accordion-content-1568303234927-what-are-the-responsibilities-of-supervisors-and-workers-" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="accordion-1568303234927-what-are-the-responsibilities-of-supervisors-and-workers-">
