<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="b026b05e-c6e5-4dc3-b8c9-2cc3ce97f4b0" >

    <p>Before undertaking any working alone or in isolation activity:</p> 
<ul> 
 <li><strong>Supervisors (e.g. chairs, academic directors, managers, faculty, principal investigator, supervising staff, etc.) are required to </strong>complete a Working Alone or in Isolation Risk Assessment to determine if working alone is strictly prohibited by law or if a safety plan is required.</li> 
 <li><strong>Workers are required to</strong> partake in this process to complete the Working Alone or in Isolation Risk Assessment.</li> 
</ul>
    





</div>
