    <h3>Working alone that is high risk and prohibited by law&nbsp;</h3> 
<p>If your risk assessment determined that the work, activities and/or tasks is high risk and prohibited by law, you will have to follow specific Ontario regulations as set out by the Ontario Occupational Health and Safety Act (OHSA). </p>
    





