<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="6098c1d6-185d-49ba-9108-6095d4fd9d5a" >

    <h3>Working alone that is high or medium risk and permissible requires a safety plan</h3> 
<p>If your risk assessment determined that the work is high or medium risk (as well as necessary or permitted), supervisors and employees must identify the risks and develop a safety plan.&nbsp;</p> 
<p>Safety plans can help ensure that workers are completing the work, activities or tasks alone or in isolation in a safe manner with adequate measures in place to identify and mitigate risks.&nbsp;</p>
    





</div>
<script>$(document).ready(function(){addCoursePopover("#6098c1d6-185d-49ba-9108-6095d4fd9d5a");});</script></div>

				

				
