<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="1e70851b-fee5-46d8-913a-404b657519f0" >

    <h2>Questions?&nbsp;</h2> 
<p>If you are a supervisor or worker/student with questions about working alone or in isolation, please contact EHS for additional support at 416-979-5000, ext. 553770 or <a href="mailto:ehs@ryerson.ca">ehs@ryerson.ca.&nbsp;</a></p> 
<p>If you have any safety or security concerns, you can also contact Ryerson Security at 416-979-5040 or <a href="mailto:security@ryerson.ca">security@ryerson.ca</a>.&nbsp;</p>
    





